mb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb50">[Wien]</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><tei:ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb11527">Großmann, Stefan</tei:ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1907-09-28_01">Schnitzler an Großmann, 28. 9. 1907</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1907-10-07_01">Großmann an Schnitzler, 7. 10. 1907</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only,
